      "data": {
        "title": "Advanced Primitives",
        "subtitle": "Bridge, script, and field are real Twilite primitives with stronger boundary, runtime, and authored-data responsibilities. Read the concept cards, inspect the working examples, then finish with the challenge and checkpoint.",
