      "data": {
        "title": "Challenge",
        "body": "1. Inspect the example bridge and describe what it imports.\\n2. Inspect the example script and explain why it stays visible as a node instead of hiding in a registry.\\n3. Inspect the field node and explain why authored data belongs there instead of being smeared into declaration or presentation.\\n4. Say when you would choose an advanced primitive instead of a basic one.",
        "difficulty": "intermediate",
        "_classBinding": {
